description: A Belarus orphanage says it has at least 23 cases, and that some of the children are "extremely ill".
title: Coronavirus: Belarus orphanage seeks help amid 'critical' outbreak
title_page: Coronavirus: Belarus orphanage seeks help amid 'critical' outbreak - BBC News
maintext: Ms Roche said the orphanage had taken measures to try to protect the children, but faced difficulties as they live in "dense" conditions in dormitories.
